Version 1.1 - released 2015-04-27
* upgraded to CodeMirror 5.2

Version 1.0 - released 2015-01-08
* updated to CodeMirror 4.10
* split stylesheet.css for easier maintenance
* changed mode for "external" editors to "php"
* added init_codeeditor_css() API

Version 1rc4 - released 2014-12-27
* fixed regression bug, where saving via keyboard shortcut was not possible
  anymore
* fixed bug, where multiple CodeMirrors on a form could still trigger multiple
  form submissions

Version 1rc3 - released 2014-12-25
* fixed bug, where usage as external editor from other plugins might have failed
  (reported by svasti)
* fixed bug, where unmodified editors triggered leave confirmation in some
  clients
* fixed bug, where instantiation of multiple editors on the same page failed
* fixed bug, where multiple codemirrors on a form could trigger multiple form
  submission
* updated to CodeMirror 4.9
* merged stylesheets
* added configurable matching and autoclosing of tags
* added some styling for the preview (inspired by svasti)

Version 1rc2 - released 2014-12-23
* made compatible to CMSimple_XH >= 1.6 and dropped support for older versions
* upgraded to CodeMirror 4.8
* enabled CTRL-s shortcut for all editors
* added Codeeditor support for editing the complete content file

Version 1rc1 - released 2013-02-11
* updated to CodeMirror 2.38
* changed configuration to be proper JSON
* implemented preview mode (for content editor only)
* added Czech and Slovak localization (contributed by oldnema resp. Tata)
* added German localization and user manual
* cleaned up and improved code
* merged and/or minified JavaScript and CSS files

Version 1beta5 - internally released 2012-12-24
* implemented possibility to use a Codeeditor with an own submit button
* fixed bug, where Codeeditor misbehaved on IE

Version 1beta4 - released 2012-09-03
* updated to CodeMirror 2.33

Version 1beta3 - released 2012-09-02
* fixed bug where external config files were not recognized (reported by svasti)

Version 1beta2 - released 2012-08-24
* updated to CodeMirror 2.22
* implemented editor interface of CMSimple_XH 1.5.2+
* switched to init.js file instead of config options for more flexibility
* implemented additional functionality (available through keyboard shortcuts)
* allowed to save without modifications (suggested by svasti)
* fixed bug: codeeditor didn't work with CMSimple_XH before 1.3
* updated manual

Version 1beta1 - released 2012-01-13
* updated to CodeMirror 2.2
* switched from implicit requirements check to explicit system check
* added several config options
* rewritten without need for jQuery
* implemented editor interface for CMSimple_XH 1.5+
* added default.php for CMSimple_XH 1.5+
* added manual
* cleaned up code
* added warning when leaving page with unsaved modifications (doesn't work in
  Opera)

Version 1dev1 - released 2011-08-21
* tag()ged <link>s
* added config option: enabled (suggested by Gert)
* fixed: highlighting fails after save
* added fullscreen mode (suggested by Gert)

Version 0.0.2 - released 2011-07-18
* removed console.log() (reported by Gert)

Version 0.0.1 - released 2011-07-18
* initial release
